reviewText: First off, there could be alot more dvd's to chose from! The DVD quality is choppy, and not as good as the VHs quality. There is no menu, Special features, surround sound, it needs a re-release already! All there is, is the movie! I found it in the wal-mart 5.50 bin, and I know why it's in there! I am a Goosebumps freak,(Be glad i'm not bragging that i'm the biggest fan) so I had to collect these!
